name: Josh L
text: Pizza is standard, some of the crust toppings are better than others, and you should bring your own utensils.

name: Tim Turner
text: My pizza was delivered with missing toppings.  When I called about it, the manager was rude and only offered a small credit ($5) off my next order.  I can accept the forgotten toppings, but because the poor customer service I received from the management I will not return to this location.
